title: Too Cute! Cotton Knits for Toddlers
description: Adorable. Delightful. Easy--and completely irresistible! Whimsical designs in bright, cheerful colors are a snap to knit because they're based on the simplest knitting stitches. ? Choose from curlicue-topped hats, darling booties with animal faces and tails, matching sweater sets, charming bloomers, and a Christmas-tree cap--14 projects in all ? Made with comfy cottons for easy care and long-lasting wear; durable enough to pass down from one child to the next ? No difficult techniques required; most trims are stitched on after you've knitted the basic shape
